graph TB
    APB[HealthTech_PatientRecords] --> DESC_ENG[HealthTech_LabAnalyzer]
    CFG[HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault] --> DESC_ENG
    CFG --> SCHED

    subgraph "Scheduler Group"
        subgraph "Descriptor Engine"
            DESC_ENG --> |desc_ar_*| DESC_AXI[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]
            DESC_AXI --> |desc_r_data| DESC_PARSE[HealthTech_PatientRecords]
            DESC_PARSE --> |descriptor_packet 256-bit| DESC_OUT[HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault]
            DESC_ENG --> |mon_valid/packet| DESC_MON[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]
        end

        DESC_OUT --> |descriptor_valid/ready| SCHED[HealthTech_LabAnalyzer]

        subgraph "Scheduler"
            SCHED --> |datard_valid/addr/beats| RD_IF[HealthTech_PatientRecords]
            SCHED --> |datawr_valid/addr/beats| WR_IF[HealthTech_EMR_Sync]
            RD_IF --> |datard_done_strobe| SCHED
            WR_IF --> |datawr_done_strobe| SCHED
            SCHED --> |mon_valid/packet| SCHED_MON[HealthTech_LabAnalyzer]
        end

        DESC_MON --> ARB[HealthTech_PatientRecords]
        SCHED_MON --> ARB
        ARB --> |mon_valid/ready/packet| MON_OUT[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]
    end

    RD_IF --> RD_ENG[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]
    WR_IF --> WR_ENG[HealthTech_PatientRecords]
    RD_ENG --> |datard_done| RD_IF
    WR_ENG --> |datawr_done| WR_IF
    MON_OUT --> SYS_MON[HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault]

    style DESC_ENG fill:#bbf,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style SCHED fill:#f9f,stroke:#333,stroke-width:3px
